      <title>亚洲企业本季度出售创纪录的 5900 亿美元本地债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/asian-firms-sell-record-590-billion-of-local-bonds-in-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于借款人利用本地融资成本比美元更便宜的优势，亚太地区的公司在第二季度出售了创纪录数量的本币债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/asian-firms-sell-record-590-billion-of-local-bonds-in-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 22:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型银行将支付 4600 万美元解决掉期勾结案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/big-banks-to-pay-46-million-to-settle-swaps-collusion-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[包括高盛集团、摩根大通和法国巴黎银行在内的十家美国和欧洲主要银行计划支付总计 4600 万美元，以结束与养老金计划的漫长法律纠纷，养老金计划指控它们合谋阻止竞争对手参与利率互换交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/big-banks-to-pay-46-million-to-settle-swaps-collusion-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 19:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“反复无常、难以预测”：为何快钱交易员喜欢特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/-volatile-and-unpredictable-why-fast-money-traders-like-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的即兴风格可能会再次让金融市场动荡不已——而这对于依靠这种风格发财的全球快钱交易者来说恰好是好事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/-volatile-and-unpredictable-why-fast-money-traders-like-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行行长豪瑟表示，仅凭单一 CPI 数据来设定利率是一个严重错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/rba-s-hauser-says-current-account-surpluses-may-not-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚储备银行二号人物安德鲁豪瑟表示，仅根据一份通胀报告来制定政策将是一个“严重的错误”，并指出未来还将公布一系列经济数据，需要进行详细的分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/rba-s-hauser-says-current-account-surpluses-may-not-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲发行人美元债券销售额创 17 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/asian-issuers-sell-14-billion-of-bonds-in-busiest-week-of-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，亚太地区美元债券销售额飙升至2023年1月以来的最高水平，因为企业和政府在利差可能进一步攀升之前锁定了历史上较窄的利差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/asian-issuers-sell-14-billion-of-bonds-in-busiest-week-of-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:30:40 GMT</pubDate>
